The paper deals with text recognition in natural images, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel architecture and loss function, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories as well. The paper also involves semantic segmentation, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper deals with text recognition, which is a problem in information retrieval, making cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a possible category.
